name: THE TICKLE - Issue #19
description:
Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers.

#19 is the 'Discontinued' Issue, our first post-H=N edition, featuring artwork by the stunningly talented Zai Divecha, Dave Greber & Slava3ngl. 

Featured writer this week is the wonderful crypto-poet and VerseVerse co-creator Kalen Iwamoto.

Created by artists Wily Guys (@guyswily) and Maia Mellier (@maiamellier)
